products.title: RedMart Instant Oatmeal
products.desc: Our Australian instant oatmeal is 100-Percent wholegrain and high in fiber. Cooks in one and half minutes makes for a quick and easy breakfast.

secondary.name: Storage Guidelines
secondary.content: Store in a cool, dry place. Once opened, transfer into an airtight container.

primary.name: How to Use
primary.content: Place 50g of oats into a large non-metallic bowl, add 300ml of cold water or mlk. Cook on full power for 1 minutes (800W) or 50 seconds (900W). Stir and then cook on a full power for a further 30 seconds (800W/900W). Leave to stand for 1 minute. Add sugar or salt to taste. Do not reheat.
